rm=\"biblScope\">8.23</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>) : freq. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author></bibl>, esp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλήλων πειρᾶσθαι</foreign>, as <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐπειρῶντο κατὰ τὸ ἰσχυρὸν ἀλλήλων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:76\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.76</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πειρᾶσθέ μου γυναικὸς ὡς ἀφράσμονος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1401\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1401</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. τῆς Πελοποννήσου</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make an attempt</tr_> on it, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:100\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.100</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. τοῦ τείχους</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:81\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.81</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n80357.10\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. gen. rei, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make proof</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">trial of</tr_>. . , <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σθένεος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:359\" defaul